      <title>Model Risk in Credit Portfolio Models</title>
      <link>https://arxiv.org/abs/2111.14631</link>
      <description>arXiv:2111.14631v2 Announce Type: replace-cross 
Abstract: Model risk in credit portfolio models is a serious issue for banks but has so far not been tackled comprehensively. We will demonstrate how to deal with uncertainty in all model parameters in an all-embracing, yet easy-to-implement way.</description>
